narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you are a senior, you will have to take this class. It is a great class that really helps you in the process of finding a topic and developing a game plan for your senior essay. It really makes the process of writing the essay less stressful than it seems to be in other departments.
This is part 1 of the Senior Essay, and you'll only take it as a senior Linguistics major.

This is essentially a semester of preparation for the senior essay. Some of my friends in other majors were jealous that we had this sort of step-by-step guidance. Raffaella is wonderful, but you probably already know that by now.
